Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:03.56,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Riko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:05.10,Main,Riko,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:17.58,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,Riko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.08,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Okay, job's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:23.41,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,You're free to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:26.33,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.59,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:31.17,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:34.93,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Because I killed Satoru Gojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.39,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:37.43,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:13.96,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Don't be so impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.11,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,The Tombs of the Star \Nand the Forbidden Vault
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:59.70,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,use barriers that conceal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.20,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,So they can't place guards at the entrances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.58,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,As long as you know where the doors are,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.16,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,they're full of holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:10.41,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Sorcerers are busy during this time of year,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.83,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,and Jujutsu High is brimming \Nwith Fly Heads right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.30,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,It's pure chaos outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:20.22,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,And since I have no cursed energy, \NI'm like the invisible man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:23.18,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,There was one problem, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:25.18,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,If I wield a cursed tool,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:29.27,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,the cursed energy from it will stop \Nme from being an invisible man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.61,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Now, there's more to this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.95,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,See, I keep a cursed spirit \Ncapable of storing objects around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.62,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,So I usually put my cursed tools \Nin it when I'm walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.70,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,You don't have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.41,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Yes, that means the cursed energy from
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:54.25,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,the cursed spirit should stop me \Nfrom being an invisible man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:01.42,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,So I make the cursed spirit smaller,\Nuntil it can fit inside my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.55,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Then I keep it inside my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:08.64,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,After all, the organs of the invisible \Nman are invisible, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:11.64,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,That's how I'm able to \Npass through any barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:14.10,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,while still carrying \Nall kinds of cursed tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:21.94,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,That's also why I didn't use \Na cursed tool at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.82,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,A surprise attack on the Six Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.41,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,would be pointless if I wasn't invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:32.00,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,I could've killed the Star Plasma Vessel first,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.54,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,but the risk of the Six Eyes seeing me was too—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.46,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.25,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,You have a Heavenly Pact, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.96,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,I know revealing information about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:42.42,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,your ability increases its fundamental \Nstrength, just like for a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.93,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,That's not what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:49.47,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,How did you know which doors \Nled to the Tombs of the Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:53.18,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,We didn't leave even \Nthe slightest residuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.87,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Humans leave plenty of \Ntraces aside from residuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:59.32,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Like scents, footprints, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.78,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,My pact enhances all five of my senses, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.86,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,There should have been \Nanother woman on the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.24,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:07.24,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.08,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Oh, that maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.62,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,She's probably dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.95,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,I didn't care if she lived or died, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.66,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,If she's lucky, she might still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.58,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.46,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,You really should... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.90,Italics,Geto,0,0,0,,That Rainbow Dragon has \Nthe toughest hide there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.10,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Curse Manipulation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.23,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Riffraff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:31.07,Main,Splitmouth,0,0,0,,Hey, am...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.83,Main,Splitmouth,0,0,0,,Am... Am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.41,Main,Splitmouth,0,0,0,,pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.25,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,A potential apparition?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.04,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,It deploys a simple domain that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:43.76,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,enforces non-violence on both of us \Nuntil I answer its question, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.59,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.42,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Then I'll just come out and say
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.69,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,you're not my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.18,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.15,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.36,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.11,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,For you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.37,Italics,Geto,0,0,0,,Curse Manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.95,Italics,Geto,0,0,0,,It's a technique that lets me \Nabsorb cursed spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.37,Italics,Geto,0,0,0,,that have surrendered, \Nand freely manipulate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:21.33,Italics,Geto,0,0,0,,If there's roughly a two-grade \Ndifference in our levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.75,Italics,Geto,0,0,0,,I skip making them submit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.92,Italics,Geto,0,0,0,,and absorb them unconditionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.78,Italics,Geto,0,0,0,,His cursed spirit may have a unique ability, \Nbut it's not that strong itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.93,Italics,Geto,0,0,0,,I can absorb it. That'll lock down his armory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.80,Italics,Geto,0,0,0,,Then I can just brute-force him—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.46,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,I didn't cut you badly enough to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.00,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,I would've killed you if \Nyou were a shikigami user,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.38,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,but since it's Curse Manipulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:15.81,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,there's no telling what might happen to the \Ncursed spirits you've absorbed after you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.78,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,I'd rather avoid extra trouble here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.02,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,You have the blessing of parentage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.77,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,But even with that blessing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:30.32,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,you were all beaten by a monkey like me \Nwho can't even use cursed techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:33.57,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,If you want to live a long life, \Nnever forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:40.04,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Oh, speaking of blessings...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.00,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,That's right. I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.21,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,I named him Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.62,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Go on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:19.17,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,The corpse of the Star Plasma \NVessel, Riko Amanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.79,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,All four limbs intact, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.84,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,Hmm, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.97,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,We'll issue your payment as we discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.10,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,I'll even throw in a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.27,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Thank you, Founder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:36.60,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,You're so generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.69,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,He's not the founder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:39.69,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.31,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:46.07,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,I know it was a necessary expense, \Nbut you've already helped us out a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:48.74,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,I thought you'd complain a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:54.03,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,We hired you for the assassination \Nexpecting that it would fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.99,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,Our Star Religious Group \Nwas founded in the Nara Era,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:59.21,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,when Tengen-sama began preaching
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:01.58,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,about the moral foundation \Nof jujutsu sorcerers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:04.16,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,a minority, as Buddhism \Nspread throughout Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.30,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,Jujutsu society and religious corporations \Nare at complete odds with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:10.55,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,That strain is what gave birth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:14.89,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,to our modern Star Religious Group, \Nthe Time Vessel Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:18.31,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,That is also why we have devoted \Nourselves to remaining non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.15,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,Jujutsu sorcerers are granted \Nmany privileges above the law,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:25.07,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,but they're still fundamentally forbidden \Nto lay a hand on non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:28.11,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,However, the time had finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:32.36,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,The time of the taboo \Nrecorded in our scriptures!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.45,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,Our Star Religious Group has evolved to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.66,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,a monotheistic religion \Nworshiping one absolute god!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:40.71,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,And it was now time for our object of \Nworship to assimilate with that impurity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.59,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,If our believers saw us simply sit back \Nand watch the assimilation happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.34,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,our Association would crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:52.59,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,Yet if we took excessive action, \Njujutsu sorcerers would crush us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:56.35,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,So we were truly desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.56,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,And how did it all turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.98,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,We thought we were going to lose everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.10,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,and now we have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:06.57,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,Of course that would \Nloosen our purse strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:14.11,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,Human society might be what crumbles \Nif Tengen-sama loses control, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:19.70,Main,Sonoda,0,0,0,,If we should perish along with our star, \Nthen that is all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:34.76,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Were you referring to Okinawa \Nwhen you said they helped us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:35.63,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:39.18,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Why didn't you kill the maid then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.59,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,I know I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:44.31,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,"Take her someplace far away, \Nand kill her at some point."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:49.07,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,Because I had a good idea of what \Nyou were planning at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:52.14,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,I made the call that the relief \Nfrom the maid's successful rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:55.99,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,would wear him down more than \Nheightened tensions from failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:12:01.94,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,You often ignore the lines of communication \Nand toss out whatever I was planning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.58,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,It all worked out in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.83,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,And stop running your mediator ragged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.59,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Yeah, but why Okinawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.88,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,I had a laugh at that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:18.05,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,Normally, you'd use a car \Nto transport a captive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:21.26,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,Public transportation carries \Ntoo many risks, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:25.81,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,But get this. The president \Nowned his own private jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.69,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:33.65,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,Rich people think on a different scale, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:35.99,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Well, let's go eat with their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:38.62,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Take me to one of the \Nrestaurants you use for clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:40.62,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.62,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,You never pay for a guy, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.41,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,I've already decided I'll only see you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:49.63,Main,Kong,0,0,0,,either for work or in Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:07.85,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:13.65,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,Hey, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.15,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.11,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,For real, real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:21.37,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,I'm alive and kicking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.56,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Reverse cursed technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.83,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:28.43,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,When you stabbed me through the throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.96,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,I gave up on counterattacking
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:32.79,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,and poured all my focus into \Nthe reverse cursed technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.46,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,Cursed energy is negative energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.68,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,While it can enhance the body, \Nit can't regenerate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:43.26,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,So you multiply that negative energy \Nagainst itself to create positive energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.02,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,That's the reverse cursed technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.85,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,Easier said than done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:49.22,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,I hadn't been able to do \Nthat up until now myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:52.81,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,And I couldn't understand anything \Nthe one person who could do it said!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.81,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,{\an8}He's blabbing on and on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:56.53,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,He's high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.48,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,But I finally grasped it \Non the verge of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.48,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,The true essence of cursed energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:05.08,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,The reason you're going to lose is \Nbecause you didn't chop my head off,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:08.75,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,and because you didn't use that cursed \Ntool when you stabbed my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.75,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,I'm going to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:15.54,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Our fight is just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.96,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,Oh? Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.47,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.26,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,Maybe so!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:36.15,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,Cursed Technique Reversal:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:39.15,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.91,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.76,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,No bones are broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.68,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,That shock wave was an \Napplication of Limitless,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:10.72,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,the cursed technique reversal, Red, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:15.19,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,So he poured the positive energy generated \Nby the reverse cursed technique
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:19.99,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,into the Limitless \Ntechnique ingrained into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:22.57,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,One, the power to stop:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.74,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,the neutral application \Nof the Limitless technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.41,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,Two, the power to attract:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:31.12,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,the amplified application of \Nthe Limitless technique, Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.58,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,And three, the power to repel:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.42,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,the reversal of his cursed technique, Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:42.33,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,All things I can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.30,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,Something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.43,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,Something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:57.44,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,No, this is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:00.98,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.47,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,Sorry, Amanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:27.47,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,I'm not even angry over you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.68,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,I bear no grudge against anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:37.70,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,It's just that the world feels \Nso, so wonderful right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:57.96,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,"Throughout Heaven and Earth, \NI alone am the honored one."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:04.67,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,The merit of having a technique \Nthat's passed down for generations
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.26,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,is having a user's manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:08.72,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,The demerit is that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.64,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,information about the\Ntechnique is easily leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:14.60,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,You were a member of \Nthe Zen'in clan, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:18.48,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,That's why you know so much \Nabout the Limitless technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.32,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,However, even in the Gojo clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.61,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,only a scant few know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.71,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,Take the amplified and the reversal,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.54,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,then smash together those \Ntwo different expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:44.21,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,of infinity to create and \Npush out imaginary mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:46.97,Italics,Gojo,0,0,0,,Imaginary Technique: Purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.56,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,Something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.48,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,"I refuse to do any work for free."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:05.11,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,Normally I would've said that \Nand hightailed it out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:10.82,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,Yet the freshly awakened wielder of the \NLimitless technique was right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:14.45,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,He was probably the strongest jujutsu \Nsorcerer of the modern age.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.20,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,I wanted to reject him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.29,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,I wanted to bring him to his knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:23.04,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,I wanted to take down the \Npinnacle of the jujutsu world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.67,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,and the Zen'in clan that rejected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:30.63,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,I twisted myself to try to affirm myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:34.68,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,That was the moment I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:46.69,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,I thought you had abandoned that pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:54.28,Italics,Toji,0,0,0,,I thought you had chosen to live without \Nrespecting yourself or anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.20,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,Any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.67,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.27,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Two or three years from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.94,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,my kid will be sold off to the Zen'in clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:24.60,Main,Toji,0,0,0,,Do what you will with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.27,Main,Storage,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:28.64,Main,Storage,0,0,0,,Hug me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:09.43,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,You're late, Suguru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:12.10,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,No, I guess you got here fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.53,0:22:16.39,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,There are several Star Religious \NGroup facilities in the city, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:20.36,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,Satoru? Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.17,0:22:22.82,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:25.49,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,I see you already saw Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:27.91,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,Yeah, she healed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:29.87,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:36.38,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,No, me being safe doesn't \Nhelp anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:38.30,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:39.75,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,You're not at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.76,0:22:41.88,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:46.01,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,Suguru, should we kill these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:49.72,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,The way I feel right now, \NI doubt I'd feel anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:54.69,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,No. There's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:22:59.06,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,It looks like there are only \Ncommon believers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:02.95,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,The masterminds who know about our \Nworld have probably fled already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:05.78,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,And unlike with the bounty,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:08.49,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,they won't be able to \Ntalk their way out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:10.91,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,The organization had \Nproblems to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:12.88,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,It'll be dissolved soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:16.17,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,No point, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.67,Main,Gojo,0,0,0,,Does there really need \Nto be any point to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.35,0:23:33.18,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,It's very important that there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:36.81,Main,Geto,0,0,0,,Especially for a jujutsu sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:42.80,Main,Shoko,0,0,0,,I wonder if whoever came up with the phrase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.80,0:23:45.07,Main,Shoko,0,0,0,,"a surprising side" \Nthought of people as cubes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:47.40,Main,Shoko,0,0,0,,and if whoever came up with the insult
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:49.83,Main,Shoko,0,0,0,,"shallow" thought of people as flat surfaces?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:51.54,0:23:54.58,Main,Shoko,0,0,0,,Either way, people do have two sides to them.
